---
title: Pork & Veggie Bolognese Risoni with Parmesan & Balsamic Rocket Salad
description: If you thought bolognese and spaghetti were a match made in heaven, wait till you try it as a saucy risotto dish! Arborio rice absorbs the well-loved flavours of the bolognese in a way that pasta can’t - we think that this twist on a classic is a 10 out of 10.

*We’ve replaced the
arborio rice in this
recipe with risoni due
to local ingredient
availability. It’ll be just
as delicious, just follow
your recipe card!*
